item.title: CVE-2023-50268|2023-12-13T20:49:54.982Z -- jqlang -- jq
item.description: jq is a command-line JSON processor. Version 1.7 is vulnerable to stack-based buffer overflow in builds using decNumber. Version 1.7.1 contains a patch for this issue.
